#: ../../docs/tutorials/shading/shading_reference/canvas_item_shader.rst:224
msgid "inout vec2 **SHADOW_VEC**"
msgstr "inout vec2 **SHADOW_VEC**"

#: ../../docs/tutorials/shading/shading_reference/canvas_item_shader.rst:224
